{"tid":1258531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蕭生：擾民抗爭令抗爭失敗；年青抗爭者前途令人擔憂，證明毓民煽動衝擊是仆街！","createTime":"2019-06-26T07:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T07:11:57.000Z","uid":219007,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"45aea4864d2d73538d7ab60220ad8c7908c1a3da","tid":1258531,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T07:07:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gCnZrAbaCHM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgCnZrAbaCHM&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=eb46447a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gCnZrAbaCHM</a><br />\n<br />\n抗爭不能太擾民，<br />\n擾民式包圍政府抗爭令市民反感。<br />\n包圍時亦應容許人出入。<br />\n<br />\n我在2014佔領時一早察覺呢點，於是在928兩日後我立即呼籲撒退，但D人唔聽，結果最初有50%支持佔領變到最尾有70%民意反對佔領，令抗爭大敗！<br />\n<br />\n煽動抗爭代價非常大，例如黃之峰呼籲圍警總及有人呼籲去銀行拎錢式抗爭等，呢D隨時坐監，我現在非常擔心年青人前途！<br />\n<br />\n所以當年我大力批評黃䋣民叫人衝立法會，他係推人去死。"},{"pid":"89871af19781fb51c4597955335abe912bda319a","tid":1258531,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T07:08:55.000Z","msg":"【召集鍵盤戰士】G20 全球洗版大行動！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1258441\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1258441</a><br />\n<br />\n工未必人人罷得到，<br />\n但鍵盤戰士咁容易做，<br />\n唔係咁都唔做啊？"},{"pid":"5ce42298f3cd69744abec0551f76e7a5a6b76516","tid":1258531,"uid":60434,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T07:09:49.000Z","msg":"燒山好野"},{"pid":"35d1ddcbf1e8232e996d4087611b6f190d91a800","tid":1258531,"uid":254371,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T07:10:39.000Z","msg":"燈神燒山再次發功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d3309693d60a7118f1dd802a12195f37c2e724","tid":1258531,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T07:11:49.000Z","msg":"切回之父 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" 